      "content": "it's just that the more people tell me to \"keep fighting\" or \"hold on,\" the more it feels like they don't actually get it. it's like they're asking me to sign up for another forty years of this. it feels less like fighting and more like just being tortured for no reason. wouldn't it be more compassionate to just let someone find peace when they've had enough? it feels like there's no dignity in just suffering forever.",
